import time

        start_sha = time.time()

        start_bcrypt = time.time()
        salt = bcrypt.gensalt()
        bcrypt_hash = bcrypt.hashpw(user['raw_password'].encode(), salt)
        writer.writerow(['Bcrypt', user['username'], time.time() - start_bcrypt, bcrypt_hash.decode()])"}
